Half of the episodes on this DVD are from other Mickey Mouse Clubhouse DVDs. My son loves the show so we have almost every DVD made and this is the first one I've noticed that is a copy of other ones. Wish I had known it would be a lot of what we already have on DVD because I would not have bought it since he could just watch the other ones. Had hoped for an entirely new DVD like they usually are. But if you don't have any other ones or if you don't mind the duplication of half the episodes then it's a good buy.
